data.description:
Excellent starter home or investor home!  home needs some TLC but is in fantastic location and school districts of Casa Grande.  Right in heart of area where you have the best parks. Everything within walking distance. Highly desirable neighborhood. Home warranty transferred to new buyer or investor and is good till January 2025!! 
All offers to be looked at by seller on 10/29/2023. Home sold as is and no further inspection periods after acceptance of offer. Cameras in place as is in process of an estate sale. Possession and coe to be after 11/9/23. Please call listing agent before writing contract to make sure all is correctly spelled out.  Seller is to be as follows: Estate of Judith Kitching,Deceased,by Miska Pearson,Personal Representative
